    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h2 style="font-family:'Gill Sans', 'Gill Sans MT', Calibri, 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;color: #D17B88;">Conclusion &#128171</h2>
            <p>Based on our survey findings, it is evident that <b>security, hygiene, and food quality are paramount considerations</b> for female residents when seeking accommodation. Furthermore, respondents expressed a <b>stronger sense of freedom when residing off-campus</b> compared to on-campus living. The influence of <b>parental opinions</b> was observed to have a <b>greater impact on hostel choices</b> compared to those opting for flat or PG accommodations. Despite these observations, the highest satisfaction level reported for current accommodations remained moderate, with a rating of 3. These insights emphasize the importance of addressing key priorities and improving residential offerings to better align with residents' expectations and enhance overall satisfaction levels.</p>

        </div>
